item.title: Client file is not working
item.dc:creator: @gimpie gimpie
item.description:
@gimpie wrote:

Change the ip in your client.java (in your client file ofcourse) to your ip, its probbably set to 127.0.0.1 or someshit, just go into your client.java and search “127.0” and it should show you it, if 127.0 isnt the right the ip then its probbably set to something else, either way its in your client.java. hope this helps
